[00:00.000]--- Lesson 13  The Greenwood Boys 绿林少年
[00:04.780]The Greenwood Boys are a group of pop singers.^“绿林少年”是一个流行歌曲演唱团。
[00:08.986]At present, they are visiting all parts of the country.^目前他们正在全国各地巡回演出，
[00:13.740]They will be arriving here tomorrow.^明天就要到达此地。
