[00:24.451]Tomorrow evening they will be singing at the Workers' Club.^明晚他们将在工人俱乐部演出。
[00:29.309]The Greenwood Boys will be staying for five days.^“绿林少年”准备在此逗留5天。
[00:33.593]During this time, they will give five performances.^在此期间，他们将演出5场。
[00:38.531]As usual, the police will have a difficult time.^同往常一样，警察的日子将不好过，
